data.description: MULTIPLE OFFERS RECEIVED, BEST AND FINAL BY SATURDAY DEC 16 AT 6PM. This beautiful 4 bed, 2.5 bath home features an addition room connected to the master suite that can serve as a bedroom, sitting area, office, or even a studio. The massive kitchen offers SS appliances with abundant cabinet space. The French patio doors open up to a patio slab ready for the new owner. The home sits in a very cozy pocket just minutes away from The Highlands, Parks Mall, many theaters, restaurants and multiple options for groceries. HWY 20, HWY 360, and HWY 287 are in very close proximity!
